Each chapter is located in a folder: chapterN

Each folder contains:

chapN.tex  the LaTeX source of the chapter
mainN.tex  a LaTeX source file that includes chapN.tex and builds a chapter, importing project and style files etc.

oldfigs/ a folder containing eps files for second edition figures, some of these are still used
newfigs/ a folder containing PDF files created for third edition, these are Python generated
ezdraw/ a folder containing eps files of line drawings, updated for third edition
figures/ a folder containing other figures, typically images, that fit none of the above categories

Makefile  a utility to support building the chapter and various other things